OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774534302
OL,3,CFamilies of those killed in Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash file complaint against MOD
OL,6,FRelatives of those killed in the 1994
OL,7,FRAF Chinook helicopter disaster have
OL,8,Ffiled a formal complaint against the
OL,9,FMinistry of Defence.
OL,11,FTwenty-five intelligence experts and
OL,12,Ffour special forces crew were killed
OL,13,Fwhen the helicopter crashed on the
OL,14,FMull of Kintyre, en route from RAF
OL,15,FAldergrove in Northern Ireland to Fort
OL,16,FGeorge near Inverness, on June 2 that
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
