PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774534302
OL,3,CFamilies of those killed in Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash file complaint against MOD
OL,6,FOn Wednesday families met with the
OL,7,FVictims Minister in Westminster and
OL,8,Fsay they're escalating their campaign
OL,9,Ffor a public inquiry.
OL,11,FThey believe it's the only way to get
OL,12,Fto the truth of what happened on the
OL,13,FScottish hillside.
OL,15,FThe crash was initially blamed on
OL,16,Fpilot error before this was overturned
OL,17,Fin 2011.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
