FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774534302
OL,3,CFamilies of those killed in Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash file complaint against MOD
OL,6,FConcerns have since emerged about the
OL,7,Fairworthiness of the helicopter, but
OL,8,Fthe Ministry of Defence has described
OL,9,Fwhat happened as an accident,
OL,10,Finfuriating relatives of those killed.
OL,12,FNevin Phoenix lost his father,
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Ian Phoenix, in
OL,14,Fthe tragedy.
OL,16,FHe expressed the depth of anger felt
OL,17,Fby families to Victims Minister Alex
OL,18,FDavies-Jones at the meeting in
OL,19,FWestminster.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774534302
OL,3,CFamilies of those killed in Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash file complaint against MOD
OL,6,FNevin Phoenix said: "The MOD are still
OL,7,Finsisting on pushing out the old lines
OL,8,Fof tragic accident.
OL,10,F"There's been six inquiries, and we
OL,11,Ftold them in that meeting how
OL,12,Foffensive and how disingenuous we find
OL,13,Fthat line, and that's appalling.
OL,15,F"The Victims Minister agreed and she
OL,16,Fhas very kindly agreed to a further
OL,17,Fmeeting and she'll be taking up with
OL,18,Fthe Prime Minister's office as well,
OL,19,Fthe MOD's actions."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
